ht: 700;">Directions</span></div><div><span style="font-weight: 700;"><br></span></div><div>1. Pour frozen blueberries and banana into blender</div><div>2. Add Wholy Dose UNFLAVORED Powder</div><div>3. Add milk, blend on high until smooth</div><div>4. Top with your favorite toppings (Madison used goji berries, hemp seeds, and bee pollen)</div><div>5. Enjoy!</div></div></div></div></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606231549091" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606231549091"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><b><br></b></p><p><b>Where can our audience find you?</b></p><p><b><br></b></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606231556391" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606231556391"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>My Instagram page is @HealthByMads, and my website is madisonmaley.com. Truly cannot believe how much the community has grown over the past year, and I hope to keep expanding both my page and my site!</p><p><br></p><p><br></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--></div><div id="divContentBk"></div><!--End_Gem_Page_Main_Editor-->
